		<title>今日の戯れ言：TPP 大筋合意 - remark</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://text.baldanders.info/remark/2015/1011-diary/" />
		<id>tag:text.Baldanders.info,2015-10-11T23:06:14+0900:/remark/2015/1011-diary/</id>
